Msunduzi Municipality has announced that its cash office and customer care centre at the AS Chetty Building at 333 Church Street will be open on Saturday and Sunday because the City will be embarking on disconnections for accounts in arrears. The office hours will be from 8am to 4pm on both days. The City said payment of accounts and reconnections can be done during these extended office hours. The contact number is 033 392 2263. Proof of payment can be emailed to paymybill@msunduzi.gov.za Residents are urged to quote their account number to insure reconnection.